  endingImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 21342434c0849b549a4425fa54b36d13, type: 3}
  endingTitle: 'Good Ending: Escape!'
  endingText: "The two sides are locked in place, neither willing to make the first
    move. Then a rocket tears out of nowhere, slamming into a hover right behind
    you \u2014 your friends, finally! One grab, a hard yank, engines screaming, and
    the whole mess just drops out from under you."
